<h1>Buffalo Chicken Pizza</h1>
<img src="https://www.halfbakedharvest.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Skillet-Crispy-Cheese-Buffalo-Chicken-Pizza-1-scaled.jpg">

<h2>Description</h2>
<p1>This Buffalo Chicken Pizza is a perfect fusion of classic pizza and spicy buffalo chicken wings. The tangy buffalo sauce paired with melty cheese and tender chicken creates a flavor explosion in every bite. Whether you're hosting a game night or just want to spice up dinner, this pizza will satisfy those who love bold, zesty flavors. Simple to make and easy to customize, it's become a favorite for pizza and wing lovers alike.</p1>

<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Chicken: Cooked and shredded chicken breast.</li>
  <li>Buffalo sauce: Your favorite brand of hot buffalo sauce.</li>
  <li>Pizza dough: Store-bought or homemade.</li>
  <li>Cheeses: Mozzarella and blue cheese crumbles.</li>
  <li>Ranch dressing: For drizzling over the pizza.</li>
  <li>Onions: Thinly sliced red onions for extra flavor.</li>
  <li>Spices: Salt, pepper, and garlic powder.</li>
</ul>
